    "updated_at": "2016-07-12T00:32:43Z",
    "body": "I think I have a solution for this but I'm not at a windows machine at the moment.  Can someone test this patch?\n\n``` diff\ndiff --git a/atom/browser/native_window.cc b/atom/browser/native_window.cc\nindex c084f44..d718bcf 100644\n--- a/atom/browser/native_window.cc\n+++ b/atom/browser/native_window.cc\n@@ -243,6 +243,9 @@ extensions::SizeConstraints NativeWindow::GetContentSizeConstraints() {\n void NativeWindow::SetMinimumSize(const gfx::Size& size) {\n   extensions::SizeConstraints size_constraints;\n   size_constraints.set_minimum_size(size);\n+  if (GetContentSizeConstraints().HasMaximumSize())\n+    size_constraints.set_maximum_size(\n+        GetContentSizeConstraints().GetMaximumSize());\n   SetSizeConstraints(size_constraints);\n }\n\n@@ -253,6 +256,9 @@ gfx::Size NativeWindow::GetMinimumSize() {\n void NativeWindow::SetMaximumSize(const gfx::Size& size) {\n   extensions::SizeConstraints size_constraints;\n   size_constraints.set_maximum_size(size);\n+  if (GetContentSizeConstraints().HasMinimumSize())\n+    size_constraints.set_minimum_size(\n+        GetContentSizeConstraints().GetMinimumSize());\n   SetSizeConstraints(size_constraints);\n }\n\n\n```\n"
